Copyright 2026 laci141 and contributors

Created by laci141 (@laci141).

This CLI queries the public, keyless Grants.gov Search2, NIH RePORTER, and
NSF Awards APIs. It is built with the Go standard library only and follows
the printed-CLI conventions of CLI Printing Press
(https://github.com/mvanhorn/cli-printing-press) by Matt Van Horn.

